er issues, worked cross-functionally to design and solve for critical processes that our teams needed to succeed, and was someone I could always rely on for helping navigate the inevitable escalations. Jessica also played an instrumental role in leading the Americas at New Relic successfully through its major transformation from a SaaS company to a Consumption business model.\n...\nAn early win\n...\nexample of strong\n...\nblend of strategic thinking along\n...\nJessica instituted business intelligence and rigor\n...\nteams find sales trends.\n...\nThese trends drove\n...\nand opportunities contributing\n...\nmy revenue growth"
